ZH: 今天早饭我吃了面包和牛奶。
EN: For breakfast today, I had bread and milk.

ZH: 妈妈每天都会准备美味的早饭。
EN: Mom prepares delicious breakfast every day.

ZH: 早饭是一天中最重要的一餐。
EN: Breakfast is the most important meal of the day.

ZH: 我们通常在家吃早饭。
EN: We usually have breakfast at home.

ZH: 健康的早饭应该包含蛋白质和纤维。
EN: A healthy breakfast should include protein and fiber.

ZH: 在中国,早饭通常包括米饭和粥。
EN: In China, breakfast usually includes rice and porridge.

ZH: 我通常在忙碌的工作日吃轻松的早饭。
EN: I usually have a light breakfast on busy work days.

ZH: 有时候我会选择出去吃早餐。
EN: Sometimes I choose to have breakfast outside.

ZH: 我最喜欢的早餐是煎鸡蛋配土豆饼。
EN: My favorite breakfast is fried eggs with hash browns.

ZH: 没有时间吃早饭是我最讨厌的事情。
EN: Skipping breakfast is the worst thing for me.

ZH: 我喜欢在阳台上吃早饭。
EN: I like to have breakfast on the balcony.

ZH: 早饭后我会喝一杯咖啡。
EN: I will have a cup of coffee after breakfast.

ZH: 今天早饭吃水果可以让你更有活力。
EN: Eating fruits for breakfast today can give you more energy.

ZH: 儿童应该吃营养均衡的早饭。
EN: Children should have a balanced breakfast.

ZH: 早饭应该是全家欢聚的时刻。
EN: Breakfast should be a time for the whole family to gather.

ZH: 星期天我经常烹饪精致的早饭。
EN: I often cook elaborate breakfast on Sundays.

ZH: 早饭后的一杯热茶很舒服。
EN: A cup of hot tea after breakfast is very comforting.

ZH: 早饭是一天中的开始。
EN: Breakfast is the beginning of the day.

ZH: 我们通常在起床后不久吃早饭。
EN: We usually have breakfast shortly after getting up.
